text: Beatriz Moreno Braganza (born 20 December 1989) is an Andorran footballer who plays as a defender. She has been a member of the Andorra women's national team. ==References== Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Andorran women's footballers Category:Andorra women's international footballers
